channel.title: [Devo] How do I change the place where you log in? [Devo]
channel.description:
Title says it all,
I searched it and couldn't find anything.
I know this is possible the most simplest question in the world, and I would know it, but I forget, mostly beacause I havn't been coding my server in a while
Anyway, if anyone know, please inform me!
Also, if you could tell me where to put it, that's be great.
Thanks!
~ Me ~

item.title: [Devo] How do I change the place where you log in? [Devo]
item.dc:creator: @si_force Si Force
item.description:
@si_force wrote:

Player.java; Search your teleporting variable, for example on an average server it is “teleportToX”, and on DeltaScape it may be; “ToX”.
